1. If the product data is relatively stable and doesn't change frequently, Option 1 might be more suitable as it reduces API requests and provides a preprocessed data structure.
2. If the product data changes frequently or requires real-time updates, Option 2 would be better as it allows you to work with the latest data without the need for preprocessing.